852
01:18:51,345 --> 01:18:54,247
That was a good move.

853
01:18:54,559 --> 01:18:56,619
Money helps.

854
01:18:56,722 --> 01:18:59,191
Unemployment allowance.

855
01:18:59,584 --> 01:19:03,248
Really used wisely.

856
01:19:32,346 --> 01:19:35,180
Tommy, Tommy!

857
01:19:36,859 --> 01:19:41,661
