You asked about
the number 539 calories.

944
01:28:40,582 --> 01:28:42,517
At reference point?

945
01:28:42,663 --> 01:28:47,499
Correct. 539 calories
at reference point.

946
01:28:47,940 --> 01:28:50,364
You have to memorize it.

947
01:28:57,678 --> 01:29:01,240
- You okay?
- Yes.

