976
01:34:23,737 --> 01:34:27,037
Sounds like Tommy's essays.

977
01:34:27,240 --> 01:34:30,472
Went to restaurant.
Drank juice. Tasty.

978
01:34:30,844 --> 01:34:32,972
Train was fun.

979
01:34:33,180 --> 01:34:36,275
Oooh God. Will I get better?
