01:38:49,035 --> 01:38:55,771
September 16th, clear sky.
Mom's exam day.

1013
01:38:57,161 --> 01:39:00,689
She said "I'd fail anyway."

1014
01:39:00,939 --> 01:39:04,706
If she'd "fail anyway",
why take it?

1015
01:39:05,955 --> 01:39:08,891
Poop mom?

1016
01:39:08,989 --> 01:39:10,355
Why no poop mom?

1017
