- Good.

1064
01:42:56,149 --> 01:42:58,550
Thought I would fail.

1065
01:42:58,685 --> 01:43:00,950
I've been telling myself that...

1066
01:43:01,154 --> 01:43:04,124
I will try again.

1067
01:43:04,324 --> 01:43:07,886
I'm crying in joy.

1068
01:43:08,294 --> 01:43:12,026
Sorry, I'm babbling.

1069
01:43:12,517 --> 01:43:17,738
- How about you?
